                            <comment id="12476051" author="mkutty" created="Tue, 27 Feb 2007 01:33:20 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Please find the attached patch to create blobs and clobs dynamically. Thanks for the functionTests/util/streams methods. Now we can get rid of the Resource.jar from mailjdbc test. Please review and if everything looks fine please commit.&lt;/p&gt;

